{"title":"Radar Roundup: Horse Cycles All Road Adventure, CDC and Bernot Caps, Laurens ten Dam’s Diverge, Inside Line Equipment Blaze/Forest Bags, 210km Solo MTB, and The Ultra Divide","link":"https://theradavist.com/radar-roundup-horse-cycles-all-road-adventure-cdc-and-bernot-caps-laurens-ten-dams-diverge-inside-line-equipment-blaze-forest-bags-210km-solo-mtb-and-the-ultra-divide/","date":1699884000000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1696\" height=\"1130\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/398138026_4546843085601140_7428180154048339499_n.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/398138026_4546843085601140_7428180154048339499_n.jpg?w=1696&amp;quality=75 1696w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/398138026_4546843085601140_7428180154048339499_n.jpg?resize=1024,682&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/398138026_4546843085601140_7428180154048339499_n.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/398138026_4546843085601140_7428180154048339499_n.jpg?resize=1335,889&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/398138026_4546843085601140_7428180154048339499_n.jpg?resize=700,466&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/398138026_4546843085601140_7428180154048339499_n.jpg?resize=1536,1023&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>Our Radar Roundup compiles products and videos from the ‘net in an easy-to-digest format. Read on below for today’s findings…<span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2500\" height=\"1667\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/HorseCyclesAug233373.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/HorseCyclesAug233373.jpg?w=2500&amp;quality=75 2500w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/HorseCyclesAug233373.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/HorseCyclesAug233373.jpg?resize=2000,1334&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/HorseCyclesAug233373.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/HorseCyclesAug233373.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/HorseCyclesAug233373.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/HorseCyclesAug233373.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/HorseCyclesAug233373.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/HorseCyclesAug233373.jpg?resize=2048,1366&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.horsebrand.co/bikes/all-road-adventure\" target=\"_blank\">Horse Cycles All Road Adventure</a> $3,150</h3>\n<p>The Road Adventure is an all-new offering from Horse Cycles. It was designed to optimize room for larger tires and gnarly terrain; this bike excels in the chunky stuff. It is designed around a slightly longer fork, with more trail, and is more stable when loaded down for touring and bike camping.</p>\n<p><strong>Specs:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>T47 oversized bottom bracket / better power transfer / low maintenance threaded cups</li>\n<li>42mm Down tube for a stiffer, more stout ride</li>\n<li>Oversized 44mm head tube with reinforcement ring for ultimate control ( tapered headtube upgrade – very popular)</li>\n<li>Syntace dropouts for a seamless aesthetic</li>\n<li>Through axle front and rear – 12mm x 142mm rear / 12mm x 100mm front</li>\n<li>Flatmount disc 1-40mm-160 rear – 160 -180 front</li>\n<li>S-bend seat stays and chainstays for tire clearance.</li>\n<li>Rack mounts</li>\n<li>Tire Clearance: 27.5 x 2.25 – 55mm x 700c +</li>\n<li>Mixture of Columbus ZONA and LIFE (STEEL) Titanium (COLUMBUS) / USA-made Ti (shown above)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>See more at <a href=\"http://www.horsebrand.co/bikes/all-road-adventure\" target=\"_blank\">Horse Cycles</a>.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"960\" height=\"960\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/o-cap-regina-u-clay_dual_960x960.jpg\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/o-cap-regina-u-clay_dual_960x960.jpg?w=960&amp;quality=75 960w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/o-cap-regina-u-clay_dual_960x960.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/o-cap-regina-u-clay_dual_960x960.jpg?resize=768,768&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/o-cap-regina-u-clay_dual_960x960.jpg?resize=700,700&amp;quality=75 700w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"960\" height=\"960\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/o-cap-janina-u-rdpt_dual_960x960.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/o-cap-janina-u-rdpt_dual_960x960.jpg?w=960&amp;quality=75 960w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/o-cap-janina-u-rdpt_dual_960x960.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/o-cap-janina-u-rdpt_dual_960x960.jpg?resize=768,768&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/o-cap-janina-u-rdpt_dual_960x960.jpg?resize=700,700&amp;quality=75 700w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"960\" height=\"960\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/o-cap-aldona-u-chck_dual_960x960.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/o-cap-aldona-u-chck_dual_960x960.jpg?w=960&amp;quality=75 960w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/o-cap-aldona-u-chck_dual_960x960.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/o-cap-aldona-u-chck_dual_960x960.jpg?resize=768,768&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/o-cap-aldona-u-chck_dual_960x960.jpg?resize=700,700&amp;quality=75 700w\" /></p>\n<div>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.cafeducycliste.com/en_us/catalogsearch/result/?field_search=search&amp;q=Bernot&amp;btn_submit=Submit\" target=\"_blank\">Cafe Du Cycliste and Bernot Caps Deadstock Re-Constructed Hats</a></h3>\n<p>Collaborating with Vilnius-based Bernot Caps, Cafe Du Cycliste took some of its headstock jerseys and upcycled them into three hats. This run is limited to only 10–20 pieces; each cap is remade in the <a href=\"https://www.bernot.lt/\" target=\"_blank\">Bernot Caps</a> workshop in Lithuania, and the construction makes maximum use of as many components of the product as possible. There are three cap profiles and you can check them all out at <a href=\"https://www.cafeducycliste.com/en_us/catalogsearch/result/?field_search=search&amp;q=Bernot&amp;btn_submit=Submit\" target=\"_blank\">Cafe Du Cycliste</a>.</p>\n</div>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2380\" height=\"1587\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/220601_specialized_unbound-0043.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/220601_specialized_unbound-0043.jpg?w=2380&amp;quality=75 2380w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/220601_specialized_unbound-0043.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/220601_specialized_unbound-0043.jpg?resize=2000,1334&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/220601_specialized_unbound-0043.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/220601_specialized_unbound-0043.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/220601_specialized_unbound-0043.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/220601_specialized_unbound-0043.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/220601_specialized_unbound-0043.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/220601_specialized_unbound-0043.jpg?resize=2048,1366&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1708\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/220601_specialized_unbound-2641-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/220601_specialized_unbound-2641-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/220601_specialized_unbound-2641-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/220601_specialized_unbound-2641-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1334&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/220601_specialized_unbound-2641-scaled.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/220601_specialized_unbound-2641-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1201&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/220601_specialized_unbound-2641-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/220601_specialized_unbound-2641-scaled.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/220601_specialized_unbound-2641-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/220601_specialized_unbound-2641-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1366&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://buycycle.com/en-us/bike/s-works-diverge-2022-35722\" target=\"_blank\">Laurens ten Dam Custom Diverge</a></h3>\n<p>Laurens ten Dam is selling is custom, one of one Specialized Diverge, painted to mimic the 1984 Team Stumpjumper on BuyCycle.com for $8,240. When it sells, he will donate 25% of proceeds to a local Dutch charity called <a href=\"https://onlyfriends.nl/\" target=\"_blank\">Only Friends</a>, an organization that offers athletes with disabilities the opportunity to participate in organized sports in their own safe and familiar environment. Laurens is an ambassador for the charity.</p>\n<p>The build list is as follows:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Specialized Diverge custom pink painted fact11r carbon (S-WORKS)</li>\n<li>Shimano GRX 815 Di2 Groupset, 48/31 x 11/24 11 speed</li>\n<li>Handlebar PRO Discover Carbon 40 with 20-degree flare. PRO bar tape.</li>\n<li>Saddle PRO Discover Carbon 142mm</li>\n<li>Seatpost PRO Discover Carbon</li>\n<li>Bottle cages PRO carbon</li>\n<li>Wheels Roval Terra 25mm inner width (the more aero version for UNBOUND)</li>\n<li>Tires brand new Specialized Pathfinder pro 42 mm. (Laurens’ go-to UNBOUND tire)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Check out more at <a href=\"https://buycycle.com/en-us/bike/s-works-diverge-2022-35722\" target=\"_blank\">BuyCycle.com</a></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/ILE_Blaze_Forest_1-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/ILE_Blaze_Forest_1-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/ILE_Blaze_Forest_1-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/ILE_Blaze_Forest_1-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/ILE_Blaze_Forest_1-scaled.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/ILE_Blaze_Forest_1-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/ILE_Blaze_Forest_1-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/ILE_Blaze_Forest_1-scaled.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/ILE_Blaze_Forest_1-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/ILE_Blaze_Forest_1-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://ilequipment.com/blogs/news/new-blaze-vx25-forest-x50-collection\" target=\"_blank\">Inside Line Equipment Blaze/Forest Collection</a></h3>\n<p>New additions to our Blaze/Forest collection: <a href=\"https://ilequipment.com/products/travel-pack?variant=43067304935601\">Travel Pack</a>, <a href=\"https://ilequipment.com/products/default-backpack?variant=43067297038513\">Default 25L</a>, <a href=\"https://ilequipment.com/products/pilot-bar-bag?variant=43067303723185\">Pilot Bar Bag</a>, and <a href=\"https://ilequipment.com/products/load-cell-cable?variant=43067304706225\">Load Cell – Cable</a>. These pieces feature a combination of Blaze VX25, Forest X50, blaze reflective tape, and tonal trim; a nicely colorblocked layout that balances high vis orange with earthy green. Not too loud, not too subtle.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"398\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/Blaze_Forest_1_2c0d7c1b-3634-49f.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/Blaze_Forest_1_2c0d7c1b-3634-49f.jpg?w=1200&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/Blaze_Forest_1_2c0d7c1b-3634-49f.jpg?resize=1024,340&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/Blaze_Forest_1_2c0d7c1b-3634-49f.jpg?resize=768,255&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/Blaze_Forest_1_2c0d7c1b-3634-49f.jpg?resize=700,232&amp;quality=75 700w\" /></p>\n<p>ILE first introduced the Blaze/Forest treatment two years ago on its <a href=\"https://ilequipment.com/products/porteur-rackbag-small?variant=41367930306737\">Porteur Rackbag – Small</a>, which led to experimenting with some <a href=\"https://ilequipment.com/blogs/news/shop-friends-jerarde-gutierrez\">one-off Travel Pack variations</a> for the shop. ILE spent the past few months fine-tuning the concept before officially expanding the lineup to include these new styles.</p>\n<p>Roll on over to <a href=\"https://ilequipment.com/blogs/news/new-blaze-vx25-forest-x50-collection\" target=\"_blank\">ILE</a> to see the full collection!</p>\n<p><em>Read John’s review of the Travel Pack here:</em></p>\n<p><em><a href=\"https://theradavist.com/inside-line-equipment-travel-pack-review/\" target=\"_blank\">There and Back Again: Inside Line Equipment Travel Pack Review</a></em></p>\n<p> </p>\n<hr />\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/e8d0d61c-dc33-435f-b141-81334177-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/e8d0d61c-dc33-435f-b141-81334177-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/e8d0d61c-dc33-435f-b141-81334177-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,768&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/e8d0d61c-dc33-435f-b141-81334177-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1500&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/e8d0d61c-dc33-435f-b141-81334177-scaled.jpg?resize=768,576&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/e8d0d61c-dc33-435f-b141-81334177-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1350&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/e8d0d61c-dc33-435f-b141-81334177-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,1001&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/e8d0d61c-dc33-435f-b141-81334177-scaled.jpg?resize=700,525&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/e8d0d61c-dc33-435f-b141-81334177-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1152&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/e8d0d61c-dc33-435f-b141-81334177-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1536&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/5ef9cbaf-8ca6-4289-a938-c30c4dcf-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/5ef9cbaf-8ca6-4289-a938-c30c4dcf-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/5ef9cbaf-8ca6-4289-a938-c30c4dcf-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,1024&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/5ef9cbaf-8ca6-4289-a938-c30c4dcf-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/5ef9cbaf-8ca6-4289-a938-c30c4dcf-scaled.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/5ef9cbaf-8ca6-4289-a938-c30c4dcf-scaled.jpg?resize=768,768&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/5ef9cbaf-8ca6-4289-a938-c30c4dcf-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1800&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/5ef9cbaf-8ca6-4289-a938-c30c4dcf-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,1335&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/5ef9cbaf-8ca6-4289-a938-c30c4dcf-scaled.jpg?resize=700,700&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/5ef9cbaf-8ca6-4289-a938-c30c4dcf-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1536&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/5ef9cbaf-8ca6-4289-a938-c30c4dcf-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,2048&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/2bbd4932-12ad-4e09-8d56-72675ecf-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/2bbd4932-12ad-4e09-8d56-72675ecf-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/2bbd4932-12ad-4e09-8d56-72675ecf-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,768&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/2bbd4932-12ad-4e09-8d56-72675ecf-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1500&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/2bbd4932-12ad-4e09-8d56-72675ecf-scaled.jpg?resize=768,576&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/2bbd4932-12ad-4e09-8d56-72675ecf-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1350&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/2bbd4932-12ad-4e09-8d56-72675ecf-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,1001&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/2bbd4932-12ad-4e09-8d56-72675ecf-scaled.jpg?resize=700,525&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/2bbd4932-12ad-4e09-8d56-72675ecf-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1152&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/2bbd4932-12ad-4e09-8d56-72675ecf-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1536&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<h3>Rad Bazaar Finds</h3>\n<p><em>We love seeing the support for our Rad Bazaar, a service we host for Group Ride members. For now, you can read all about how to sign up for the <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/the-radavist-group-ride-subscription-plan-and-rad-bazaar/\" target=\"_blank\">Group Ride and Rad Bazaar here</a>.</em></p>\n<div>\n<div><strong><a href=\"https://radbazaar.theradavist.com/listing/BM2hbRH6tmLBYhW8trNv?category=undefined&amp;subcategory=undefined\" target=\"_blank\">2023 Tanglefoot Hardtack (med) Frameset</a> $750</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>Very lightly ridden this summer. Includes FSA headset and salsa clamp, along with thru axles. Size is medium, I’m 5’9 with 30in inseam and it fits well…a little less standover than I’m used to. Has a little scrap on chain stay from another bike rubbing during travel. Also has all sorts of mounts and is ready for any adventure or even just a plain old bike ride with Gramps. Price is $750 US fun-tickets. I will ship from Buffalo and will split costs with you or you can pick up. Check out the details at Analog bikes in lovely Vermont.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><strong><a href=\"https://radbazaar.theradavist.com/listing/EEmSXSa4463it9AsgvAI?category=undefined&amp;subcategory=undefined\" target=\"_blank\">1985 Ritchey Timber Comp</a> $2000</strong></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>A 1985 hand-built Ritchey mountain bike, filet brazed by Tom. Timber Comp model, 18” with Roller Cam brakes, in great condition. Local pickup only from Mill Valley, CA.  <strong>SOMEONE JUMP ON THIS ONE!</strong></div>\n<div></div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><strong><a href=\"https://radbazaar.theradavist.com/listing/QxCzmjwlP88eOKJ4IorR?category=bikes&amp;subcategory=undefined\" target=\"_blank\">1984? Specialized Stumpjumper</a> $1500</strong></div>\n<div></div>\n<div>Early (1984?) Specialized Stumpjumper in beautiful condition. All-original parts. Patina.</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div></div>\n<hr />\n<p> </p>\n<div><span><span>﻿</span>﻿</span><span>﻿</span></div>\n<p> </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=A4vmiFGy4aU\" target=\"_blank\">Racing a 210km Solo MTB Ride in 1 Day | Lakeland 200 FKT</a></h3>\n<p>The Lakeland 200, nestled within the awe-inspiring landscapes of the Lake District in the UK, beckons as more than a mere adventure; it’s a pilgrimage of self-discovery. Covering a formidable 200 miles of diverse terrain, this epic odyssey is an invitation to explore the limits of endurance, skill, and tenacity. It’s a journey that calls to those who dare to venture beyond, and its origins are as remarkable as the route itself…</p>\n<p> </p>\n<div><span><span>﻿</span>﻿</span><span>﻿</span></div>\n<p> </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=utYq8hMGc_0\" target=\"_blank\">Bikepacking Iceland: The Ultra Divide</a></h3>\n<p>A south to north, 600km bikepacking adventure through the highlands of Iceland.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<hr />\n<p> </p>\n<h3>Radavision</h3>\n<p>Stuff we see on the ‘net that causes pause…</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1696\" height=\"1130\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/398138026_4546843085601140_7428180154048339499_n.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/398138026_4546843085601140_7428180154048339499_n.jpg?w=1696&amp;quality=75 1696w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/398138026_4546843085601140_7428180154048339499_n.jpg?resize=1024,682&amp;quality=75 102